&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Lead execution of seller initiatives and team projects from proposal through to measurement&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
