&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;The Lead of Operations Quality &amp;amp; Performance will be required to work on-site every day in our local warehouse. The Lead will be required to conduct internal audits to assess adherence to GOAT Group’s standards, compile results into a data-driven report, and provide feedback to the leadership team. Based on audit findings, the Lead is expected to execute training sessions that will improve process accuracy, depending on each department’s needs. Additionally, the Lead is expected to review and analyze the weekly Quality Performance report to identify trends and areas of opportunity to discuss with each facility.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
