&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Receive and arrange inbound inventory according to brand, model, etc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Keep detailed notes and enter accurate data into the GOAT Group database, including release information, product SKUs and production dates&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Continuously research and learn about new models and brands of sneakers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Manage and keep up to date with the authentication process through training and self-directed learning&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Other duties as assigned&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
