&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;The Supervisor, Authentication is responsible for the management and day-to-day strategy of the Authentication team. You’ll partner with Operations leadership to develop a plan for continued growth and development and ensure SLA compliance while upholding our quality and safety standards.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
