&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Be responsible for day-to-day operations, quality control &amp;amp; supervision of the Authentication team, including actively communicating in the Slack channels, informal daily check in&#39;s, coaching on performance and assisting with scheduling needs of the Authentication team, as needed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Execute and track operational goals and is responsible for troubleshooting performance issues related to Cost Per Order (CPO)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Foster a culture of safety, teamwork and continuous learning by upholding GOAT&#39;s quality and safety standards and ensuring SLA compliance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Be responsible for the day-to-day people management and development of the Authentication team, including coaching employees to meet operational goals, performance management and training.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Work cross-functionally to drive Quality Control expectations within Authentication&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Support tracking and troubleshooting order issues, e.g. misverification reports, and audits to support the team. Act as the last line of defense for any order issues&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Work in a dynamic warehouse environment with heavy equipment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;2+ years of supervisory or leadership experience with a background in product authentication&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Knowledge of and passion for sneakers and apparel, including familiarity with industry trends and resources&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Strong attention to detail, problem-solving and decision-making skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt

